Blog rewind: LSU holds on to beat UF Florida v LSU Chris Graythen / Getty Images BATON ROUGE, LA - OCTOBER 17: Leonard Fournette #7 of the LSU Tigers runs for a first down past Marcus Maye #20 of the Florida Gators at Tiger Stadium on October 17, 2015 in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. (Photo by Chris Graythen/Getty Images) ORG XMIT: 573703781 BATON ROUGE, LA - OCTOBER 17: Leonard Fournette #7 of the LSU Tigers runs for a first down past Marcus Maye #20 of the Florida Gators at Tiger Stadium on October 17, 2015 in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. (Photo by Chris Graythen/Getty Images) ORG XMIT: 573703781 (Chris Graythen / Getty Images) Orlando Sentinel 
The Gators look to improve to 7-0 on the season against Leonard Fournette and the Tigers.
